{
  "stem": "23730.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she, she was crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was saying, I should have given you two potatoes a day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we speak in German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I told, her never mind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You saved our life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, never mind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You gave us a potato.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You saved us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know whether she heard me because of that clattering going out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were already leaving the farm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was our experience the first few days marching through Silesia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Eventually, we went as far as Dessau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, we had to stop in Friedland concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And those were terrible days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But eventually, we reached the railway station of Dessau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there, we were put into open goods trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then Helmut, the guard, was running up and down the platform, looking for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Imagine that.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There already other hundreds of prisoners joined the train, not only the 500.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he found me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was nearly dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Ernest!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Ernest!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Ernst!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Ernst!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Ernst!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he threw me a round-- half of  a round loaf into the-- and I caught it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Certainly, they all went for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was left with very little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But still, what a mensch he was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He found me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Ernst!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Ernst-- gave me bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- they, they tore it from me in seconds, these people, right, [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never-- again, never-- can you imagine that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not one of these wonderful people could I detect after the war, because just Helmut, finished.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What interest [? to me was ?] his second name?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't-- look, I was 19.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't so practical yet, right?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the train journey from Dessau was-- we were covered in snow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had open wagons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somewhere at the Elbe, this train stopped, because there was some bombardment going on-- some, some air raid somewhere.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
